OL,3,CMan who used spray paint to deface
OL,4,Cchurch jailed
OL,6,FA man who used spray paint to deface a
OL,7,Fchurch in Leyland has been sentenced.
OL,9,FIn April, Joseph Williams, 31, daubed
OL,10,Fmore than 20 gravestones at St James's
OL,11,FChurch in Leyland with paint,
OL,12,Fincluding offensive images and
OL,13,Fderogatory comments about God.
OL,15,FHe also spray-painted the gate of a
OL,16,Fnearby property and on the following
OL,17,Fday, 20 April 2025, he targeted
OL,18,Fseveral vehicles with similar imagery.
