OL,3,CMan who used spray paint to deface
OL,4,Cchurch jailed
OL,6,FA window at St Mary's Church was also
OL,7,Fdamaged and several cars in the area
OL,8,Fhad similar images and language daubed
OL,9,Fon them.
OL,11,FOn 27 April 2025, police were alerted
OL,12,Fto a male who had smashed a window at
OL,13,FSt Marys Church. Williams was stopped
OL,14,Fand arrested on West Paddock soon
OL,15,Fafter.
OL,17,FDuring a house search, police
OL,18,Frecovered two bags that Williams was
OL,19,Fseen holding at the church containing
OL,20,Fa hammer and two bottles containing
OL,21,Fpetrol.
