OL,3,CMan who used spray paint to deface
OL,4,Cchurch jailed
OL,6,FSeveral cans of spray paint were also
OL,7,Fdiscovered at his home address.
OL,9,FOn Wednesday 5 November 2025, Williams
OL,10,Fwas sentenced at Preston Crown Court
OL,11,Fto eight months in prison, after he
OL,12,Fadmitted two counts of religiously
OL,13,Faggravated criminal damage and eight
OL,14,Fcounts of criminal damage.
OL,16,FClare Byers, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,17,Ffor CPS North West said: "Joseph
OL,18,FWilliams deliberately targeted
OL,19,Fchurches in his local area which has
OL,20,Fshocked and saddened the local
OL,21,Fcommunity.
