OL,6,F"He gave no thought to those that
OL,7,Fworship at the churches or the
OL,8,Ffamilies of those laid to rest there.
OL,10,F"I hope those affected can feel some
OL,11,Fsense of justice knowing Williams will
OL,12,Fface the consequences of his
OL,13,Fdisrespectful, hateful actions.
OL,15,F"There is no place for hate in our
OL,16,Fsociety."
OL,18,FThe Reverend from St James's Church
OL,19,Fwas made aware of the damage on Good
OL,20,FFriday.
