OL,6,FHis victim personal statement was read
OL,7,Fto the court which outlined the shock
OL,8,Ffelt by the Reverend after seeing a
OL,9,Fsacred place of worship desecrated,
OL,10,Fespecially on a religious day.
OL,12,FThe Reverend explained he has spent
OL,13,Fsome nights after that walking around
OL,14,Fthe churchyard to protect it from
OL,15,Ffurther damage.
