OL,6,FHe also outlined how grateful he was
OL,7,Fto the community, local workmen and
OL,8,Fthe council who all helped to put
OL,9,Fthings right in time for a wedding the
OL,10,Ffollowing day and religious services
OL,11,Fover Easter.
OL,13,FThe parish Priest from St Mary's
OL,14,FChurch also made a victim personal
OL,15,Fstatement which was read to the court.
OL,17,FHe spoke about his shock and grave
OL,18,Fconcern for the parish community as a
OL,19,Fresult of the crime.
